and favor. O Allah, my Lord, uproot the transgression, and rip the ropes of oppression into pieces, and make the markets of mischief and wrongdoings stagnant, and dignify those who dislike them, and pull the foundations of the tyrants from its root, and make them face loss and defeat after their luxuries, and hasten O Allah in attacking them while they unaware, and send Your wrath upon them, and put the evildoers and corrupted ones to death, so that those who fear them feel at peace, and the sorrowful and saddened men feel relieved, and the hungry is filled, and those things that are on the verge of destruction are saved, and the evaders gain shelter, and the vagrants return, and the poor become rich, and the seekers of peace attain it, and the old men are honored, and the infants are pitied, and the oppressed gain dignity, and the oppressors become humiliated, and the sorrowful are relieved, and the difficulties are solved, and the mutinies are calmed, and the differences end, and knowledge gains elevation, and peace and harmony becomes widespread, and conflicts and diversities turn into unity, and faith is strengthened, and the Holy Qur’an is recited, indeed You are the remunerator, the Sustainer, and the Graceful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ رَبِّ فَابْتُرِ الظُّلْمَ، وَبُتَّ حِبَالَ الْغَشْمِ، وَاَخْمِدْ سُوْقَ الْمُنْكَرِ، وَاَعِزَّ مِنْ عَنْهُ یَنْزَجِرُ، وَاحْصُدْ شَافَۃَ اَهْلِ الْجَوْرِ، وَاَلْبِسْهُمُ الْحَوْرَ بَعْدَ الْكَوْرِ، وَعَجِّلِ اللّٰهُمَّ اِلَیْهِمُ الْبَیَاتَ، وَاَنْزِلْ عَلَیْهِمُ الْمُثَلَاتِ، وَاَمِتْ حَیَاۃَ الْمُنْكَرِ لِیُؤْمَنَ الْمَخُوْفُ، وَیَسْكُنَ الْمَلْهُوْفُ، وَیَشْبَعَ الْجَائِعُ۔ وَیَحْفَظَ الضَّائِعُ، وَیِاوَی الطَّرِیْدُ، وَیَعُوْدَ الشَّرِیْدُ، وَیُغْنَی الْفَقِیْرُ، وَیُجَارَ الْمُسْتَجِیْرَ، وَیُوَقَّرَ الْكَبِیْرُ، وَیُرْحَمَ الصَّغِیْرُ، وَیُعَزَّ الْمَظْلُوْمُ، یُذَلَّ الظَّالِمُ، وَیُفَرَّجَ الْمَغْمُوْمُ، وَتَنْفَرِجَ الْغَمَّائُ، وَتَسْكُنَ الدّهَمَائُ، وَیَمُوْتِ الْاِخْتِلَافُ، وَیَعْلُوَا الْعِلْمُ، وَیَشْمَلَ السِّلْمُ، وَیُجْمَعَ الشَّتَاتُ، وَیَقْوَی الْاِیْمَانُ، وَیُتْلَی القُرْآنُ، اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ الدَّیَّانُ الْمُنْعِمُ الْمَنَّانُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19"